{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@preconcurrency","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"flatMap","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"SegmentOfResult","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@Sendable","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci7ElementQa","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncSequence/Element"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"async","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SegmentOfResult","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency28AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequenceV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"Self","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SegmentOfResult","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SegmentOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AsyncSequence","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An error-throwing mapping closure. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"accepts an element of this sequence as its parameter and returns an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AsyncSequence"},{"type":"text","text":". If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an error, the sequence ends."}]}],"name":"transform"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A single, flattened asynchronous sequence that contains all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements in all the asynchronous sequences produced by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"sequence ends either when the last sequence created from the last","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"element from base sequence ends, or when ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"text":" throws an error.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to receive a single-level asynchronous sequence when your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transformation produces an asynchronous sequence for each element.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this example, an asynchronous sequence called "},{"code":"Counter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" produces "},{"code":"Int","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values from "},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"code":"5","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The transforming closure takes the received "},{"code":"Int","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and returns a new "},{"code":"Counter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" that counts that high. For example, when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transform receives "},{"code":"3","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" from the base sequence, it creates a new "},{"code":"Counter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that produces the values "},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"2","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"code":"3","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The "},{"code":"flatMap(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“flattens” the resulting sequence-of-sequences into a single"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"AsyncSequence","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". However, when the closure receives "},{"code":"4","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", it throws an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error, terminating the sequence."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["do {","    let stream = Counter(howHigh: 5)","        .flatMap { (value) -> Counter in","            if value == 4 {","                throw MyError()","            }","            return Counter(howHigh: value)","        }","    for try await number in stream {","        print(number, terminator: \" \")","    }","} catch {","    print(error)","}","// Prints \"1 1 2 1 2 3 MyError() \""]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingMapSequence"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["/documentation/swift/asyncthrowingmapsequence/flatmap(_:)-53stf"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},